{
  "texts": [
    "Aguirre and Zavala (2013), for example, developed a tool to assess the mathematics lesson plans based on mathematical thinking, language, culture, and social justice.",
    "Similarly, Jacobs et al. (2008) developed a model to assess lesson plans developed by science teachers.",
    "Ndihokubwayo et al. (2022) also developed a lesson plan analysis tool that assessed the lesson plans of competence-based curriculum.",
    "The current study, however, evaluates the lesson plans based on learning theories and models in addition to the use of technology integration.",
    "The theoretical framework of this study is based on learning theories such as behaviorism and constructivism."
  ]
}